y bohot rahem waale jis se rahem maanga jaata hai, rahem kar meri kamzoori aur be-basee par aur mujhe is dard se aafiyat de.", "Urdu": "اے ہر دینے والے سے زیادہ سخی اے بہترین ذات جس سے مانگا جاتا ہے اے بہت رحم والے جس سے رحم مانگا جاتا ہے رحم کر میری کمزوری اور بے بسی پر اور مجھے اس درد سے عافیت دے۔", "RArabic": "YAA AJ-WADA MAN A’TAA YAA KHAIRA MAN SO-E-LA WA YAA AR-HAMA MENAS TUR-HEMA IRHAM ZA’FAA WA QIL-LATA HEE-LATEE WA A’FE-NEE MIN WAJA-AA’.", "ArabicText1": "يَا اَجْوَدَ مَنْ اَعْطٰى يَا خَيْرَ مَنْ سُئِلَ وَيَا اَرْحَمَ مَنِ اسْتُرْحِمَ اِرْحَمْ ضَعْفٰى وَقِلَّةَ حِيْلَتِىْ وَاَعْفِنِىْ مِنْ وَجَعٰى۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15